data.description: Welcome to your new home! This impressive 5-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom residence is a masterpiece of design, offering a spacious and well-thought-out layout. Nestled in a prime location with access to top-rated schools, this property caters to both practicality and beauty.  Both HVAC systems have been replaced, roof is only 3 years old, new paint throughout and a new BEAUTIFUL patio!! Key Features:  **5 Bedrooms**: Generously sized bedrooms provide comfort and privacy for every family member or guest.  **3.5 Bathrooms**: Stylishly designed bathrooms with modern fixtures and finishes add a touch of elegance.  **Prime Location**: Conveniently located near essential amenities, shopping centers, and entertainment options. **Top-Rated Schools**: Enjoy the peace of mind that comes with residing in an excellent school district, ensuring a quality education for your children. **Spacious Dining Room**: Host memorable dinners in the large dining room, perfect for gatherings and celebrations. **Great Room**: The great room provides a cozy and inviting space for relaxation and entertainment. **Sunroom as Eat-in Kitchen**: The sunroom serves as a delightful eat-in kitchen, bringing in ample natural light for a refreshing dining experience.  **Gourmet Kitchen**: The well-equipped gourmet kitchen boasts high-end appliances, generous counter space, and stylish cabinetry. **Private Outdoor Space**: Retreat to your private backyard, an ideal spot for outdoor activities or quiet moments. **Wet bar in the Basement.  Great additional entertaining area!  Contact me today to schedule a viewing and envision the possibilities of making this house your home!
